		<descript>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
			<abstract>
New York City Subway WiFi Locations, 2026 is a point theme representing WiFi access points in the New York subway system as of 2026. This dataset was derived from the New York State data repository (at https://data.ny.gov/Transportation/MTA-Wi-Fi-Locations/pwa9-tmie/about_data) in March 2026. Columbia Libraries staff has provided the data in the geopackage format in state plane coordinates, and a codebook and a has been included in the download package.
			</abstract>
